&lt;p&gt;A fat bumblebee stocks up on pollen from the plants in the main glasshouse at Glasgow Botanic Gardens.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/people/sayran/"&gt;Sayran&lt;/a&gt; posted a photo:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/sayran/4513064458/" title="Lake Lanier North Georgia, sunset"&gt;&lt;img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2085/4513064458_912da1c7c3_m.jpg" width="240" height="160" alt="Lake Lanier North Georgia, sunset" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Beautiful day on lake lanier today at sunset, no clouds but the sky was on fire for few minutes. Lots of haze and pollen for the last few days.&lt;br /&gt;
