&lt;p&gt;Today I participated in a World Wide Photowalk organized by Jonathan Sugarman.  A very HOT HUMID day but a wonderful time nonetheless.  &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
I got to meet up and chat with &lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/28082535@N02/" target="new"&gt; Paul &lt;/a&gt; who I had not seen for a few months since meeting up at the merchant.  &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
I got to walk with part of my class mates Xception and we had a great day.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Thanks Johathan for organizing this!  I am looking forward to next year!&lt;/p&gt;

